  <!-- EN: Wolfein Mega Corp -->
  <Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.label>沃芬族軍工巨型企業</Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.label>
  <!-- EN: MegaCorp, officially known as the Wolfein MegaCorp, handles all aspects of a Wolfein's life, from birth to death. As the name suggests, its primary focus is on developing the military-industrial sector to satisfy the board's endless expansion demands. -->
  <Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.description>沃芬軍工巨型企業，包攬了沃芬族從出生到死亡的所有業務。正如其名，該企業的主要業務方向是發展軍工產業，以滿足董事會無止境的擴張需求。</Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.description>
  <Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.fixedName>沃芬軍工巨企</Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.fixedName>
  <!-- EN: Regional Supervisor -->
  <Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.leaderTitle>區域主管</Wolfein_Faction_MegaCorp.leaderTitle>
