  <!-- EN: Wolfein Resistance army -->
  <Wolfein_Faction_Rebel.label>沃芬抵抗軍</Wolfein_Faction_Rebel.label>
  <!-- EN: The Wolfein Resistance Army is primarily driven by the goal of overthrowing the MegaCorp』s rule over the Wolfein people. Its members come from all walks of life—ranging from former corporate employees to hardened criminals—truly a reflection of the entire society. Rumors even suggest that some high-ranking figures within the ResistanceArmy are descendants of the old royal bloodline. Ultimately, due to their extreme methods of pursuing 「justice,」 the ResistanceArmy holds a poor reputation even among Wolfeins themselves. But then again, the Wolfein people don』t have many choices left. -->
  <Wolfein_Faction_Rebel.description>沃芬族抵抗軍，其核心訴求是推翻軍企對沃芬族的統治。組織內人員成分複雜，從前任軍企員工到重刑犯都有，可謂是囊括社會百相。甚至有傳言抵抗軍部分高層人員是舊世代皇族。總而言之，因為激進的聲明正義方式，使得抵抗軍即使在沃芬族內部也沒有好名聲，但沃芬族的選擇可沒有那麼多。</Wolfein_Faction_Rebel.description>
